urdu transliteration text:
Maadar ye bain karti thi dil may hai ye kasakSughra tumhari godh se aaghoshe qabr takAsghar ko maut ne kahin rukne nahi diyaYe wo ali hai jisko kabhi ghar nahi mila
Death did not let Asghar stop anywhere
@HujjatELC

Galiyon may shehre koofa ki bazaare shaam mayShireen ke ghar kabhi kabhi darbare shaam mayMarne ke baad bhi ali asghar safar may thaYe wo ali hai jisko kabhi ghar nahi mila
Even after his death, Asghar kept travelling
@HujjatELC

Nanhe se sar ko yaas se bas takte rehte thayPhir khoon roke sayyede sajjad ye kehte thayMai wo ali hoo jiska bhara ghar ujad gayaYe wo ali hai jisko kabhi ghar nahi mila
I am the Ali whose entire household got destroyed
@HujjatELC

Jaane laga watan jo ghareebon ka kaarwanMur mur ke kehti jaati thi ek khaali godh maaRakhiyo sambhaal kar isay ay arze nainawaYe wo ali hai jisko kabhi ghar nahi mila
The mother kept turning back and saying
@HujjatELC
